</div>
</div>
<button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top:20px;">Simpan Perubahan</button>
</form>
</div>


<div class="settings-section">
<h3>
<svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" style="vertical-align:middle;margin-right:6px;color:var(--yellow)"><path d="M5 3l14 9-14 9V3z"/></svg>
Teks Running / Marquee
